158
00:09:16,220 --> 00:09:17,580
This is Shi Yi's husband.

159
00:09:17,740 --> 00:09:19,460
Professor Zhousheng Chen.

160
00:09:20,180 --> 00:09:22,820
This is Du Feng, my friend.

161
00:09:23,740 --> 00:09:24,260
Hi.

162
00:09:24,420 --> 00:09:24,860
Hi.

163
00:09:27,420 --> 00:09:28,180
What's this?

164
00:09:28,740 --> 00:09:31,140
A liquor made by the locals. Smells good.

165
00:09:34,820 --> 00:09:36,700
Sorry, I don't drink.

166
00:09:37,220 --> 00:09:38,220
As a man

167
