181
00:10:13,420 --> 00:10:14,340
I'll drink for him.

182
00:10:15,260 --> 00:10:17,060
She's the one who doesn't drink at all.

183
00:10:19,540 --> 00:10:20,780
That's true love.

184
00:10:21,220 --> 00:10:22,300
Absolutely true love.

185
00:10:22,620 --> 00:10:23,620
They're married.

186
00:10:23,620 --> 00:10:24,540
How can it not be true love?

187
00:10:25,060 --> 00:10:25,900
True.

188
00:10:26,700 --> 00:10:28,460
After all, they are a family now.

189
00:10:29,740 --> 00:10:30,660
I'm the outsider.

190
00:10:31,220 --> 00:10:33,220
Whatever, let's eat.

191
00:10:40,700 --> 00:10:41,340
Eat.

192
00:10:41,500 --> 00:10:43,260
Don't drink on my behalf in the future.

193
00:10:44,180 --> 00:10:44,860
I'm willing to.

194
00:11:21,260 --> 00:11:22,540
You're strange.

195
00:11:23,180 --> 00:11:25,300
Neither do you want to leave, nor do you want to look for them.

196
00:11:27,500 --> 00:11:28,820
I don't want to bother them.

197
00:11:29,940 --> 00:11:31,140
I don't want to go back either.

198
00:11:31,820 --> 00:11:32,940
In this family,

199
00:11:33,180 --> 00:11:33,780
I like Chen and Shi Yi

200
00:11:33,900 --> 00:11:35,340
