Why not?

229
00:12:47,460 --> 00:12:48,620
Your husband is finally back.

230
00:12:48,820 --> 00:12:50,180
You should quickly live a normal life.

231
00:12:51,140 --> 00:12:52,460
We got to work. I'm going.

232
00:12:52,940 --> 00:12:53,700
-Bye-bye.
-Bye-bye.

233
00:12:53,700 --> 00:12:54,460
Bye.

234
00:12:59,340 --> 00:13:00,060
Are you drunk?

235
00:13:00,620 --> 00:13:02,380
No, I'm sober.

236
00:13:03,820 --> 00:13:04,740
Try walking on your own.

237
00:13:05,180 --> 00:13:05,940
All right.

238
00:13:10,380 --> 00:13:10,940
