242
00:13:22,700 --> 00:13:23,740
Didn't you come here before?

243
00:13:25,420 --> 00:13:27,500
Yes, I was here for work last time.

244
00:13:27,660 --> 00:13:28,700
I didn't have much fun.

245
00:13:29,580 --> 00:13:31,260
You just said you were moving out, right?

246
00:13:32,100 --> 00:13:32,780
That's right.

247
00:13:32,980 --> 00:13:33,980
Her husband is back.

248
00:13:34,140 --> 00:13:35,660
I should move out.

249
00:13:36,420 --> 00:13:38,260
