599
00:36:46,940 --> 00:36:47,790
that's always open.

600
00:36:48,010 --> 00:36:49,060
You could go there and check it out.

601
00:36:50,490 --> 00:36:52,220
Do you have a car?

602
00:36:53,390 --> 00:36:54,430
If only you came sooner.

603
00:36:54,460 --> 00:36:55,520
My wife just

604
