00:42:33,860 --> 00:42:34,340
Yes.

686
00:42:35,020 --> 00:42:36,380
Then there aren't enough sockets.

687
00:42:36,820 --> 00:42:38,340
I'll go to the supermarket downstairs later

688
00:42:38,460 --> 00:42:39,540
and buy a bigger one.

689
00:42:40,980 --> 00:42:42,100
The supermarket downstairs?

690
00:42:42,980 --> 00:42:45,100
Otherwise there will be no place to plug in the lamp.

691
00:42:46,660 --> 00:42:47,910
Okay, I got it.

